{"tid":1034624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天津商販好殘忍　用金魚巴西龜做「活吊飾」","createTime":"2019-02-24T05:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T05:33:51.000Z","uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9caa5efe2c93376286077b699ee2328ef734f505","tid":1034624,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAzxpUB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAzxpUB.png&h=6911a6e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左圖：巴西龜「活吊飾」；右圖：金魚被密封。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n天津不少商販近日把活的小金魚、巴西龜，裝進密封的塑膠袋做成吊飾，裏面僅有營養液和氧氣，每個售價5至10元人民幣。當地市民炮轟商販太殘忍，不少人買吊飾後放生。而專家表示，這種巴西龜一旦放生，將會對本地生態造成破壞。<br />\n<br />\n這種活魚、活龜吊飾在一些小作坊裏制作，裏面有顏色的液體是營養液，袋子裏還充著氧氣。一名檔主說，很多小童買這種吊飾，學校門口生意特別好。此外，一些年輕人也會買「活吊飾」，掛在車裏或是家中。檔主聲稱小金魚或者巴西龜至少活5、6個月，不用餵食，也不用換水。<br />\n<br />\n「其實是看這些小動物太可憐了，被裝在一個這麼小的袋子裏，根本活動不開，所以想買來放生。」有顧客慨嘆殘忍，6成購買者表示會將這些小動物養起來，另外4成市民則打算去放生。<br />\n　<br />\n當地水產專家表示，吊飾是密封的，即使有營養液，水的溶氧量只夠用17個小時，魚、龜一兩天就會死掉。「同時這種小烏龜不適合放生，牠是巴西龜，屬於入侵物種，會對本地的生態造成破壞。看到這樣的販賣，只要大家不去購買，這種殘忍的商品自然就會消失。」<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20140619/bkncn-20140619134509533-0619_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140619%2Fbkncn-20140619134509533-0619_05011_001.html&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=da783486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20140619/bkncn-20140619134509533-0619_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmy6umO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frmy6umO.png&h=5e30b35a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeWf68v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeWf68v.png&h=0a2cdc97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4PRehnzNzjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4PRehnzNzjM&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=713158ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4PRehnzNzjM</a>"},{"pid":"033e7ef89db85de152645a7ebde72be3fb881d38","tid":1034624,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"外國打拼十年.jpg<br />\n大陸打拼十年.jpg<br />\n香港打拼廿年.jpg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2083b3c4902aa79a8c5f34a619acfbe47a512a5","tid":1034624,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23273c14ce3509862888b42842fd0865c7551d00","tid":1034624,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"等睇放生撚表演"},{"pid":"5173729ddacb00b1d44780918b118747bd082f33","tid":1034624,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23273c14ce3509862888b42842fd0865c7551d00","tid":1034624,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"等睇放生撚表演"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"連登好似無"}]}